=== Emotional Lability and Mood Dysregulation
<subsec:emotional-lability>

*Clinical Presentation.*

    - Easy crying or emotional overwhelm
    - Irritability and low frustration tolerance
    - Rapid mood shifts
    - Difficulty regulating emotional responses
    - Emotional symptoms worsening with fatigue

*Mechanism.*
Emotional regulation requires prefrontal cortex function and adequate neurotransmitter availability. Energy deficit impairs executive control over emotions, leading to lability.
